Class PayRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.paypal.adaptive.api.requests.PayRequest

public class PayRequest
extends java.lang.Object

The request to initiate a Payment. You can use the Pay API operation to make simple payments, chained payments, or parallel payments; these payments can be explicitly approved, preapproved, or implicitly approved.
